snippet.title: Jrago The Demon Hunter - Summer Promo
snippet.description: Jrago The Demon Hunter is a METROIDVANIA style 2d platforming role playing game. The world is overcome in darkness, and you are a hunter named Jrago on a quest to slay the demons and bring back the light!
